Column Name	        Data Type	    Description

project_id	        INT	            Unique identifier for the project (Primary Key)
name	            VARCHAR(100)	Name of the project
description	        TEXT	        Description of the project
start_date	        DATE	        Start date of the project
end_date	        DATE	        End date of the project
status	            VARCHAR(20)	    Status of the project (e.g., "In Progress", "Completed", "On Hold")
manager_id	        INT	            ID of the project manager (Foreign Key referencing Users table)
created_at	        TIMESTAMP	    Timestamp when the project was created
updated_at	        TIMESTAMP	    Timestamp when the project was last updated